name: TYR Reaper Diamondfit Swimsuit - Women's
description: A streamlined suit that offers coverage and won’t interfere with your hydrodynamics. From training for your first triathlon, to just fitting in a few laps, the Reaper Diamondfit swimsuit offers a 360 degree range of motion.TYR Durafast Elite™ polyester is chlorine and fade resistant.Fabric provides UPF 50+ sun protection.Full lining has an antimicrobial treatment.Flexible straps and keyhole back allow complete freedom of movement.
